title: Noah Garfinkel
description: Noah Garfinkel (comedian! writer! Totally J/K with Joe Mande!) is hilarious. And thoughtful. And weird. So: perfect. A great episode with a true weirdo (and a weirdo! like, he listens to the show!) that Pete enjoyed so much and hopes you do, too! HOORAY, WEIRDOS!
